1
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:47,080
The Grand Princess is too bold.

2
00:00:47,560 --> 00:00:49,890
She wouldn't even spare the young prince.

3
00:00:51,160 --> 00:00:52,960
My aunt has been in the court for many years

4
00:00:52,960 --> 00:00:54,020
and has deep roots.

5
00:00:54,440 --> 00:00:56,760
Even Left Chancellor Zhou Hong is her man,

6
00:00:56,760 --> 00:00:58,560
so she has always been arrogant.

7
00:00:59,360 --> 00:01:02,800
So when she led an expedition against the Yueying Tribe,

8
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:05,090
you were powerless to stop her,

9
00:01:05,480 --> 00:01:06,440
right?

10
00:01:07,840 --> 00:01:09,560
You know it.

11
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:13,560
Of course I know.

12
00:01:13,560 --> 00:01:14,640
I'm not a fool.

13
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:18,560
I need to quickly help you gain real power,

14
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:20,560
so you can help me kill the Grand Princess

15
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:22,220
and I can complete my mission.

16
00:01:23,080 --> 00:01:24,160
Then tell me,

17
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:26,080
what do you know?

18
00:01:26,760 --> 00:01:29,560
Currently, the Grand Princess's

19
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:31,160
most important forces in the court

20
00:01:31,160 --> 00:01:32,280
are Zhou Hong

21
00:01:32,600 --> 00:01:33,800
and Eunuch Sun.

22
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:35,320
Among them,

23
00:01:35,759 --> 00:01:37,560
one is a spy planted

24
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:38,820
by your side for years,

25
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:42,479
and the other is a treacherous official hindering you in the court.

26
00:01:42,479 --> 00:01:44,960
Now that Eunuch Sun is dead,

27
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:46,880
your biggest obstacle in the court

28
00:01:46,880 --> 00:01:48,520
is Zhou Hong.

29
00:01:50,759 --> 00:01:51,840
Indeed not a fool.

30
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:56,490
Why do I feel like you're insulting me?

31
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:59,420
I'm praising your intelligence.

32
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:02,680
By the way,

33
00:02:03,000 --> 00:02:04,530
I think our top priority now

34
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:08,000
should be to win over Chancellor Shen as soon as possible.

35
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:10,960
Chancellor Shen is extremely proud

36
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:13,420
and has some complaints about me as a tyrant.

37
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,890
I can't even summon him.

38
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,440
How can I win him over?

39
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:19,360
Can't you summon him,

40
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:22,360
or do you not have the heart to?

41
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,160
Si Xingxuan.

42
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,800
Have you ever thought about it?

43
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,320
If you keep hesitating,

44
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:37,360
there will be many more victims like the Yueying Tribe

45
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:39,290
and the young prince in the future.

46
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,360
Do you have the heart to see that?

47
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:44,340
I really can't summon him,

48
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:48,240
and I really don't have the heart to.

49
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:53,760
I have a way.

50
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,720
Sister Xiaoyue.

51
00:03:17,200 --> 00:03:20,079
Are you and Ayan the best friends in the world?

52
00:03:20,079 --> 00:03:21,000
Of course.

53
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:24,400
Then Ayan will let you play with this.

54
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:28,440
This is the little tiger Auntie gave Ayan.

55
00:03:34,720 --> 00:03:36,920
When you went to her place yesterday,

56
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:39,050
did she make things difficult for you?

57
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:41,680
Why would she make things difficult for Ayan?

58
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,540
Let me tell you,

59
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,880
Auntie's courtyard is so big.

60
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,240
She even asked Ayan

61
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:49,100
if I wanted to stay there forever.

62
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:52,240
She also said she'd take Ayan to the border to play.

63
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,000
Silly child.

64
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,930
Good thing we rescued Ayan in time.

65
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:59,160
Otherwise, if he were abducted,

66
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:01,490
he'd even help Si Xinglan count the money.

67
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:04,520
Your Highness.

68
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,440
Mr. Shen, you're here.

69
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:10,240
Greetings, Your Highness.

70
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,240
Hello, Mr. Shen.

71
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,960
How are your studies going?

72
00:04:13,400 --> 00:04:14,060
My studies?

73
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,960
Let's not talk about that.

74
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:18,690
Let me show you the toy my royal brother bought me.

75
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:19,560
Hmph.

76
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:22,160
It's bad enough that he is so debauched.

77
00:04:22,400 --> 00:04:23,040
Now you are even

78
00:04:23,040 --> 00:04:24,970
leading the little prince astray.

79
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,920
Prime Minister Shen, you can teach the little prince.

80
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:31,520
I won't disturb you anymore.

81
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:34,340
You can't take it away.

82
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:44,720
Little prince, what do you want to learn today?

83
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:47,120
Writing.

84
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:48,680
Okay.

85
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:04,170
Brother.

86
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,160
Greetings, Your Majesty.

87
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,640
Since Your Majesty is here,

88
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:11,800
I will come back later to tutor you.

89
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:13,760
Minister Shen,

90
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,720
why do you seem to be avoiding me?

91
00:05:17,520 --> 00:05:18,600
Do you dislike me?

92
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:21,100
Your Majesty is the Son of Heaven.

93
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:23,000
How would I dare to avoid you?

94
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:24,120
Teacher.

95
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:25,000
Hyah!

96
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:29,400
Ayan, how improper!

97
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:35,120
Teacher, I need your help

98
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,960
to clean up the court's discipline

99
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:38,400
and restore peace to the people.

100
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:40,520
You are the one who neglects state affairs and skips morning court.

101
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:44,360
You are also the one who kills innocents and does nothing.

102
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:48,200
And now Your Majesty says you want to restore peace to the world.

103
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:53,100
Please don't mock this old minister, Your Majesty.

104
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:58,000
I beg you to trust me this once, Teacher.

105
00:06:00,080 --> 00:06:02,210
I and the millions of people in Donglin

106
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:03,680
need you.

107
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:26,320
Why did you come to see me today?

108
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,800
I recently found out

109
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:30,720
that the Emperor and Shen Qingyan are in close contact.

110
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,850
I came specially to report this to you.

111
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:33,920
Really?

112
00:06:34,320 --> 00:06:36,320
I wouldn't dare lie to you.

113
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:37,680
Didn't you say

114
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:39,080
that old fool Shen Qingyan

115
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:40,640
couldn't be bought?

116
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:44,640
Perhaps His Majesty used some trick.

117
00:06:44,640 --> 00:06:45,640
He can use tricks.

118
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:46,880
Can't you?

119
00:06:47,159 --> 00:06:47,640
Useless!

120
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:48,120
I

121
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:51,580
will submit a memorial to send him to provide disaster relief.

122
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:03,160
How dare they slander you like this!

123
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:09,000
Unless Prime Minister Shen personally provides disaster relief,

124
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:11,560
otherwise it's just an excuse

125
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:13,920
to embezzle funds under the guise of disaster relief.

126
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:16,320
These ministers are talking sheer nonsense.

127
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:18,640
It's just a tactic to have you killed.

128
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:20,920
I'm afraid

129
00:07:22,720 --> 00:07:24,450
that if you leave the palace...

130
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:28,520
Your Majesty, Prime Minister Shen is here.

131
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:37,800
Your Majesty, I have heard about what happened today.

132
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:39,200
I volunteer to go

133
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:41,600
to the extreme cold regions for disaster relief,

134
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:45,000
to protect the people and ensure their peace and prosperity.

135
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:47,560
The journey for disaster relief is long

136
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:48,960
and extremely perilous.

137
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,120
The Grand Princess's people

138
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,320
have been watching you.

139
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:52,320
I do not permit it.

140
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,080
But now, the disaster relief funds

141
00:07:54,080 --> 00:07:55,800
have been fully distributed,

142
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,720
yet somehow,

143
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,560
the number of refugees keeps growing.

144
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,760
If this continues,

145
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:03,040
I fear it will spark a riot.

146
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:04,320
Then send someone else.

147
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:06,000
Your Majesty, you know

148
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,800
that in the entire court,

149
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,920
I am the only one who can do this.

150
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:13,160
Whether Your Majesty permits it

151
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:14,480
or not,

152
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,320
I must go.

153
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,000
If I back down,

154
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:21,200
millions of victims will truly have no way to survive.

155
00:08:25,200 --> 00:08:26,720
Even if you are killed by the Grand Princess's people

156
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,760
the moment you leave the palace,

157
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,720
are you willing to risk that?

158
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:32,179
Even at the cost of my life,

159
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,600
I must go.

160
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:37,460
I have tried to win over Shen Qingyan many times.

161
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:39,159
But in the end,

162
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:41,280
he took the Emperor's side.

163
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:44,200
He really doesn't know what's good for him.

164
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:48,200
Then make sure he doesn't return.
